claim.claim-text:
Flexible coil array (2), for a magnetic resonance imaging apparatus, for indicating a loading state of a flexible coil element (1) when being positioned on at least one inductive element, the flexile coil array (2) comprising

at least one flexible coil element (1) configured for being positioned on at least one inductive element;

frequency generating means configured to generate a magnetic frequency signal;

measuring means configured to measure the magnetic frequency signal which is received by at least one coil element (1); and

signal means (3) configured to emit, for each of the flexible coil elements (1) of the flexible coil array (2), a human perceptible signal, wherein properties of the human perceptible signal are generated dependent on properties of the measured magnetic frequency signal; or

comprising any of the features of the flexible coil element (1) according to any of the preceding dependent claims.
